{
  "symptoms": "I have chest pain and shortness of breath with irregular heartbeat"
}

###

### Multiple specialties
POST http://localhost:3000/symptom-checker
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symptoms": "I have headache, dizziness and my eye vision is blurry"
}

###

### No match
POST http://localhost:3000/symptom-checker
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symptoms": "I feel very tired and have weight gain"
}